Class GraphQLDirective

  • java.lang.Object
    • graphql.schema.GraphQLDirective
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GraphQLNamedSchemaElement, GraphQLSchemaElement
    @PublicApi
public class GraphQLDirective
extends java.lang.Object
implements GraphQLNamedSchemaElement
    A directive can be used to modify the behavior of a graphql field or type. See http://graphql.org/learn/queries/#directives for more details on the concept.
